<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
    <title>GM Build Counts</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header'); %>
    <div class="custom-container">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <h2 class="pt-4" style="font-weight: bold;">Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    Visit the <a href="/vehicles" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;"><i class="bi bi-car-front-fill me-1"></i>Vehicles</a> page. Some filters may take some time to complete, wait for one filter to finish before selecting the next.
